OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775837470
OL,3,CKey moments in the Artemis II mission
OL,4,Cso far
OL,6,FThe Artemis II mission is historic in
OL,7,Fmany ways - in what it's done, how it
OL,8,Fwas done, and who did it.
OL,10,FThe four astronauts are preparing to
OL,11,Fsplash down on Earth, ending their
OL,12,Fhistoric 10-day mission, which reached
OL,13,Ffurther than any human has gone before.
OL,15,FIt will be a precise operation that
OL,16,Frequires every detail to go to plan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
