PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775837470
OL,3,CKey moments in the Artemis II mission
OL,4,Cso far
OL,6,FThe Orion capsule will reach speeds of
OL,7,Fup to 23,839 mph, burning at a blazing
OL,8,Fheat of 2,760 degrees Celsius, before
OL,9,Fit deploys 11 parachutes and lands in
OL,10,Fthe Pacific Ocean.
OL,12,FITV News explains some of the key
OL,13,Fmoments of the mission.
OL,15,FLosing contact with Nasa
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
