PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775837470
OL,3,CKey moments in the Artemis II mission
OL,4,Cso far
OL,6,FThe far-side of the moon
OL,8,FThe astronauts were tasked with
OL,9,Fphotographing the far-side of the
OL,10,Fmoon, which is usually hidden from
OL,11,Fview.
OL,13,FThey were the first human eyes to ever
OL,14,Fsee some parts of the far side,
OL,15,Fincluding its craters and lava plains.
OL,17,F"Something about you senses, 'that is
OL,18,Fnot the moon that I'm used to
OL,19,Fseeing,'" mission specialist Christina
OL,20,FKoch said at the time.
OL,26,@yD@AOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
