PN,31511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775837470
OL,3,CKey moments in the Artemis II mission
OL,4,Cso far
OL,6,FThat appeared to partially unclog the
OL,7,Fpipe, allowing the capsule to expel
OL,8,Fsome of the urine from the tank into
OL,9,Fspace.
OL,11,FMission control then informed the
OL,12,Fastronauts that the toilet was "go"
OL,13,Fbut "for fecal use only".
OL,15,FHours later the crew were given the
OL,16,Fall clear.
OL,18,F"Breaking news," mission control's
OL,19,Fcapsule communicator Jacki Mahaffey,
OL,20,Ftold the crew. "You are go for all
OL,21,Ftypes of use of the toilet."
